kind: AdaptiveDialog
modelDescription: |-
  This topic helps users define their social media strategy by identifying their primary campaign goals (e.g., Awareness, Engagement, Conversions, Web visits) and selecting the platform they want to focus on (e.g., Instagram, LinkedIn, Facebook, X (Twitter), YouTube). It is triggered when the agent needs to guide the user through a structured process to refine their campaign strategy. The agent initiates this topic when users ask for help with social media planning or strategy recommendations.

  Trigger phrases:
  "Help me with social media."
  "What's a good strategy for LinkedIn?"
  "How do I improve engagement on my posts?"
